Tileset File (.tls) Block Diagram
.-----------------------------------.
|    Signature (54h 4Ch 53h 00h)    |
|-----------------------------------|
|           Atlas  Header           |
|            (20  bytes)            |
|                                   |
|-----------------------------------|
|            Tile  Table            |
|          (Variable size)          |
|                                   |
|-----------------------------------|
|            Atlas  Data            |
|          (Variable size)          |
|                                   |
'-----------------------------------'

Atlas Header
.-----------------------------------.
|       Tile Width  (4 bytes)       |
|-----------------------------------|
|       Tile Height (4 bytes)       |
|-----------------------------------|
|      Atlas Columns (4 bytes)      |
|-----------------------------------|
|       Atlas Rows  (4 bytes)       |
|-----------------------------------|
| Offset To Start Of Atlas (4bytes) |
'-----------------------------------'

Tile Table
.-----------------------------------.
|    Number of Tiles  (4 bytes)     |
|-----------------------------------|
|              Tile  0              |
|          (Variable size)          |
|-----------------------------------|
|              Tile  1              |
|          (Variable size)          |
|-----------------------------------|
|                 .                 |
|                 .                 |
|                 .                 |
|-----------------------------------|
|              Tile  N              |
|          (Variable size)          |
'-----------------------------------'

Tile
.-----------------------------------.
|      Size Of Tile  (4 bytes)      |
|-----------------------------------|
|   Number of Keyframes (4 bytes)   |
|-----------------------------------|
|    Keyframe 0 index (4 bytes)     |
|-----------------------------------|
|   Keyframe 0 duration (4 bytes)   |
|-----------------------------------|
|    Keyframe 1 index (4 bytes)     |
|-----------------------------------|
|   Keyframe 1 duration (4 bytes)   |
|-----------------------------------|
|                 .                 |
|                 .                 |
|                 .                 |
|-----------------------------------|
|    Keyframe N index (4 bytes)     |
|-----------------------------------|
|   Keyframe N duration (4 bytes)   |
'-----------------------------------'

